headline: Humana Inc. to Present at the 2026 Leerink Partners Global Healthcare Conference
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., February 26, 2026--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) announced today that Jim Rechtin, President and Chief Executive Officer, and Celeste Mellet, Chief Financial Officer, will make a presentation to investors at the Leerink Partners Global Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, March 10, 2026, at 10:40 a.m. Eastern time.

headline: 3 Reasons HUM Has Explosive Upside Potential
summary: What a brutal six months it’s been for Humana. The stock has dropped 41.1% and now trades at $175.98, rattling many shareholders. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
